---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-tan/60 bg-surface">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-md">
        <p class="font-serif text-lg text-ink">Last Thread Co.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">
          For the men who wear things out.
        </p>
      </div>
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm">
        <a href="/guides" class="text-ink hover:text-accent">Guides</a>
        <a href="/journal" class="text-ink hover:text-accent">Journal</a>
        <a href="/about" class="text-ink hover:text-accent">About</a>
        <a href="/disclosure" class="text-ink hover:text-accent">Disclosure</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-ink hover:text-accent">Privacy</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 max-w-2xl text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted">
      Last Thread Co. is a participant in affiliate programs, including the
      Amazon Services LLC Associates Program. We earn a small commission on
      qualifying purchases made through links on this site. It costs you
      nothing and it keeps the lights on. We only link to things we'd be
      comfortable giving to our own fathers.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-8 text-xs text-muted">
      &copy; {year} Last Thread Co. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
